{
  "text": "The G\u03b2\u03b3 subunit of heterotrimeric G proteins has been demonstrated to participate in Gi-and Gq/11-coupled receptor ERK1/2 activation [CITATION_1] . In this study, we revealed that, upon activation of FFA1 by LA, Gq/11 plays a central role in ERK1/2 activation.",
